# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# 1. Copy this file: cp .env.example .env
# 2. Open .env and fill in your values
# 3. Keep .env.example in git, but add .env to .gitignore (already done)
# 4. Never commit .env with real credentials!
#
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# GETTING YOUR API KEYS
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# OPENROUTER_API_KEY:
#   1. Visit https://openrouter.ai
#   2. Click "Sign Up" or "Sign In"
#   3. Go to "Keys" section
#   4. Copy your API key (sk_xxxx...)
#   5. Paste into OPENROUTER_API_KEY above
#   6. It's free! You get free credits with sign up
#
# MONGO_URI:
#   1. Visit https://mongodb.com/cloud/atlas
#   2. Create a free account
#   3. Create a new cluster (free tier)
#   4. Click "Connect" button
#   5. Copy connection string
#   6. Replace <username> and <password> with your credentials
#   7. Paste into MONGO_URI above
#
# CLERK_SECRET_KEY (optional):
#   1. Visit https://dashboard.clerk.com
#   2. Create account and application
#   3. Go to API Keys section
#   4. Copy Secret Key
#   5. Paste into CLERK_SECRET_KEY above
#
